Abstract Jena JDBC implementation of a prepared statement

    • JenaPreparedStatement

      public JenaPreparedStatement(String sparql, JenaConnection connection, int type, int fetchDir, int fetchSize, int holdability, boolean autoCommit, int transactionLevel) throws SQLException
      Creates a new prepared statement
      Parameters:
      sparql -
      connection - Connection
      type - Result Set type for result sets produced by this statement
      fetchDir - Fetch Direction
      fetchSize - Fetch Size
      holdability - Result Set holdability
      autoCommit - Auto-commit
      transactionLevel - Transaction Isolation level
      Throws:
      SQLException - Thrown if there is a problem preparing the statement
